					</p>
					<a href="#book" class="w-full md:w-auto text-center px-10 py-4 bg-green-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">Book a Walk Today</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		
